### 1️⃣ Register Vendor
POST http://localhost:3000/common-api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Vendor",
  "email": "vendor@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "vendor",
  "phone": "1234567890"
}

### 2️⃣ Login Vendor
POST http://localhost:3000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vendor@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3️⃣ Create Restaurant
POST http://localhost:3000/restraunt-api/registerrestaurant
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pizza Hut",
  "location": "New York",
  "category": ["veg"],
  "variety": ["north-indian"],
  "offer": "20% off",
  "image": "https://example.com/pizza.jpg"
}

### 4️⃣ Add Product 
POST http://localhost:3000/product-api/addproduct
Content-Type: application/json

